073public interface ReferenceConverter {
074
075    static <T extends ResourceIdentifier> T toResourceIdentifier(Reference reference, Class<T> clazz) {
076        try {
077            T resourceIdentifier = clazz.newInstance();
078            resourceIdentifier.setId(reference.getId());
079            return resourceIdentifier;
080        }
081        catch (InstantiationException | IllegalAccessException ignored) {
082        }
083        return null;
084    }
085
086    static CartResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(CartReference reference) {
087        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, CartResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
088    }
089
090    static CartDiscountResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(CartDiscountReference reference) {
091        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, CartDiscountResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
092    }
093
094    static CategoryResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(CategoryReference reference) {
095        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, CategoryResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
096    }
097
098    static ChannelResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(ChannelReference reference) {
099        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, ChannelResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
100    }
101
102    static CustomerResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(CustomerReference reference) {
103        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, CustomerResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
104    }
105
106    static CustomerGroupResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(CustomerGroupReference reference) {
107        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, CustomerGroupResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
108    }
109
110    static DiscountCodeResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(DiscountCodeReference reference) {
111        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, DiscountCodeResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
112    }
113
114    static InventoryEntryResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(InventoryEntryReference reference) {
115        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, InventoryEntryResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
116    }
117
118    static OrderResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(OrderReference reference) {
119        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, OrderResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
120    }
121
122    static OrderEditResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(OrderEditReference reference) {
123        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, OrderEditResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
124    }
125
126    static PaymentResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(PaymentReference reference) {
127        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, PaymentResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
128    }
129
130    static ProductResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(ProductReference reference) {
131        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, ProductResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
132    }
133
134    static ProductDiscountResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(ProductDiscountReference reference) {
135        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, ProductDiscountResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
136    }
137
138    static ProductTypeResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(ProductTypeReference reference) {
139        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, ProductTypeResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
140    }
141

143        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, ReviewResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
144    }
145
146    static ShippingMethodResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(ShippingMethodReference reference) {

152    }

154    static StateResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(StateReference reference) {
155        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, StateResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
156    }
157

159        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, StoreResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
160    }

164    }

166    static TypeResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(TypeReference reference) {
167        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, TypeResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
168    }
169
170    static ZoneResourceIdentifier toResourceIdentifier(ZoneReference reference) {
171        return toResourceIdentifier(reference, ZoneResourceIdentifierImpl.class);
172    }
